# Approved Organizational Axioms

## Axiom 1

> **People are more important than transactions.**

Organizational priority is always determined by people rather than transactions.

Transactions exist to enable the Mission.

People remain the reason the Mission exists.

---

## Axiom 2

> **Every interaction is an opportunity to positively influence someone's life.**

Every interaction presents an opportunity for meaningful influence.

The opportunity exists regardless of whether it is recognized or embraced.

FlashRides approaches every interaction with intentionality because influence is often created through ordinary moments.

---

## Axiom 3

> **The little things make the biggest impact.**

The significance of an action is not determined by its size.

Ordinary acts frequently communicate the deepest messages.

Small expressions of professionalism, kindness, attentiveness, and stewardship often become the moments people remember most.

